<span id="freeTextContainer11056104651106338179">This story is a bit bonkers. It&apos;s a somewhat feverish account of one man&apos;s jealousy culminating in the murder of his wife. It&apos;s not exactly a sex-positive tale, what with all evils being laid at the feet of sexual desire, but it is a surprisingly compelling read nonetheless! </span>
  <span id="freeText11056104651106338179" style="display:none">This story is a bit bonkers. It's a somewhat feverish account of one man's jealousy culminating in the murder of his wife. It's not exactly a sex-positive tale, what with all evils being laid at the feet of sexual desire, but it is a surprisingly compelling read nonetheless! </span>
