<div id="review_1242206495" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1242206495" />
    <a title="Sandy " class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/10715774-sandy"><img alt="Sandy " src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1623855367p2/10715774.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1242206495?book_show_action=true">Mar 31, 2015</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Sandy " class="user" itemprop="url" name="Sandy " href="/user/show/10715774-sandy">Sandy </a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/10715774-sandy?shelf=audiobook">audiobook</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/10715774-sandy?shelf=source-librivox">source-librivox</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/10715774-sandy?shelf=in-translation">in-translation</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/10715774-sandy?shelf=2015-read">2015-read</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/10715774-sandy?shelf=1850-1899">1850-1899</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/10715774-sandy?shelf=classics">classics</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/10715774-sandy?shelf=pg-count-100-199">pg-count-100-199</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/10715774-sandy?shelf=womens-issues">womens-issues</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/10715774-sandy?shelf=intntl-russia">intntl-russia</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1242206495" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2952857917189493926">Disbelief. That is what I felt as I read this book. These are the ramblings of a twisted mind and a tortured soul. It is dripping with confusion and contradictions, oozing frustration and self-loathing, seething with anger and jealousy. It is no wonder that the relationship portrayed in this story ended in murder. How tragic. How horrifying. How realistic?</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

